content.description:
Straight passthrough of application data from Guidewire’s ai table to stage load. This table will be a truncate and load of incremental data.

We will want to join to advrxxchangedbeans on systemid and cmmcontainer in the source query to limit the data to incremental records. As  part of this, we’ll need to add $$m_strtdt and $$m_enddt to the mapping as parameters and add as a join condition against adddt and addtm as well.
content.name: cdi_map_acx_ai_bronze_additional_interest_application_stg_ld

transformations.name: tgt_additional_interest_application_stg

object.customQuery:
SELECT ai.systemid,
       ai.parentid,
       ai.cmmcontainer,
       ai.id,
       ai.sequencenumber,
       ai.interestcd,
       ai.interesttypecd,
       ai.AccountNumber ,
       ai.interestformcd,
       ai.interestname,
       ai.comments,
       ai.additionalcomments,
       ai.status,
       ai.preferreddeliverymethod,
       ai.escrowind,
       ai.futurestatuscd,
       ai.equipmentdescription,
       ai.underlyingpolicyidref,
       ai.underlyingaiidref,
       ai.interestdesc,
       ai.automaticind,
       ai.rowid,
       ai.billmortgrnwlind
FROM   ai
WHERE  ai.CMMContainer = 'Application';
